Ref: https://scrimba.com/p/p4Mrt9/cQnMDHD

Class based components:
1. These are important to maintain the state of react components.
2. We use constructor to do so.

Function based components: (hooks)
1. useEffect is mainly used to create side effects in the program (replacement to lifecycle methods)
2. useState is used to set and update the state of the program
3. setInterval and clearInterval are used as componentDidUnmount